caption.p: ( A, B) Effect of carvacrol and thymol combination in cell death induction through non-apoptotic pathways. Relative expression of genes related to autophagy ( A) and necrosis ( B) cell death pathways. The levels of statistical significance as done by Anova test were set at p < 0.05 (*), p < 0.01 (**) and p < 0.001 (***). ns: no significant.
